title: JankyOfYLSTE on Being a Blood, Signing to Schoolboy Q & More
description:
Janky talks about his come up, humble beginnings, the streets, Schoolboy Q and more!

----
00:00 Intro
0:31 - Just got done fighting a case for him to be able to see his son
10:19 - Going to private school off dads street money, grandfather being T Rodgers 
11:12 - Never considering selling d*pe because after seeing the negative effects on people
12:17 - How he started being a Blood, getting a college offer for football, getting hurt and starting to rap in high school 
15:52 - Defining YLSTE, it being a label, feeling like he’s overlooked, BSG proving that people are going to like what they like 
17:55 - Schoolboy Q liking Drakeo, Tee Rodgers being in Training Day with Denzel Washington 
19:50 - Schoolboy Q hitting him up on Instagram on a random morning, FaceTiming to prove it was real, Schoolboy signing him 
25:34 - Meeting Kendrick, Schoolboy preferring mornings studio session 
32:40 - Q developing him as an artist, being in every studio session, not being a regular LA rapper 
36:12 - Being in the rooms that got him ready for the success to come, having a different type of motivation 
39:57 - Introducing Seventeen Hundred and Gweezy, Gweezy being his uncle even though their one year apart in age 
44:50 - Not making regional music, being in a learning process, continuously dropping music 
47:35 - Being in session with YG, Nelly, people he’s met in the industry being genuine, LA-based artist hating 
51:00 - New projects, Instagram
